Popular radio personality Redi Tlhabi's husband Dr Brian has lost his cousin to Covid-19. The opinionated broadcaster shared the news on her Twitter account, expressing shock, as her husband's cousin according to her, didn't have pre-existing conditions. She said he was a bubbly and healthy person. She tweeted: "I obviously take the valid stats you are quoting. Our family was not so lucky. Our healthy, bubbly middle-aged cousin (56) with no pre-existing conditions, died from Covid last night. I will reserve further details until the daily national update". ALSO READ:SHIMZA'S RESPONSE BREAKS MZANSI